p: PK parameters are summarized in Table 2. The co-primary PK endpoint of relative systemic exposure by AUC 0–10 indicated higher total systemic exposure in the FD group (Table 2). The least squares ratio of geometric means for FD versus WB AUC 0–10 was 1.43 (90% CI 1.32, 1.54), which is outside of predefined equivalence bounds.
